blood on wolf mountain , also known as the wolf hill , bloodbath in &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and bloodshed on wolf mountain , is a chinese film directed by acclaimed &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; film director fei mu . made just prior to the commencement of full-scale war with imperial japan , the film itself is often considered an allegory of conflict between china and japan that had been going on intermittently since the invasion of &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in 1931 . the film was produced by the lianhua film company and was released in november of 1936 .